\frac{1}{2}\big\{\frac{1}{1}-\frac{1}{3}+\frac{1}{3}-\frac{1}{5}+\frac{1}{5}-...-\frac{1}{2n-1}+\frac{1}{2n-1}-\frac{1}{2n+1}\big\}
