 \frac{n}{2n+1} \ + \ \frac{1}{(2n+1) \ (2n+3)}  \ = \ \frac{n \ (2n+3) \ + \ 1}{(2n+1) \ (2n+3)} \ = \ \frac{  2n^2 + 3n +  1}{(2n+1) \ (2n+3)}  
= \ \frac{  (2n + 1) \ (n + 1)}{(2n+1) \ (2n+3)} \ = \ \frac{ n + 1}{ 2n+3} \ = \ \frac{(n + 1)}{2(n+1) + 1} \ \ .
